<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sesión expirada - CoromotoAccess</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #2c3e50;
            --primary-soft: rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.1);
        }

        .bg-primary {
            background-color: var(--primary) !important;
        }

        .bg-primary-soft {
            background-color: var(--primary-soft) !important;
        }

        .text-primary {
            color: var(--primary) !important;
        }

        .divider {
            width: 80px;
            height: 3px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .icon-shape {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        section {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .card {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            border-color: var(--primary);
            padding: 10px 24px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

            .btn-primary:hover {
                background-color: #1a2530;
                border-color: #1a2530;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section class="py-8 position-relative overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Fondo decorativo -->
        <div class="position-absolute top-0 start-0 w-100 h-100" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%); z-index: -1;"></div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="card shadow-lg">
                        <div class="card-body p-5 text-center">
                            <div class="icon-shape bg-primary-soft text-primary mb-4 mx-auto">
                                <i class="fas fa-clock fs-2"></i>
                            </div>

                            <span class="badge bg-primary-soft text-primary mb-3">Sesión finalizada</span>
                            <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3">Sesión <span class="text-primary">Expirada</span></h2>
                            <div class="divider bg-primary mb-4"></div>

                            <p class="text-muted mb-4">Tu sesión en CoromotoAccess ha finalizado por inactividad. Para continuar disfrutando de nuestros servicios, por favor inicia sesión nuevamente.</p>

                            <div class="d-flex mb-4">
                                <div class="me-3">
                                    <span class="icon-shape bg-primary text-white" style="width: 32px; height: 32px;">
                                        <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                                    </span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-start">
                                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">Tu seguridad es importante para nosotros</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <a href="@Url.Action("InicioSesion", "Login")" class="btn btn-primary mt-3">
                                <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt me-2"></i> Iniciar sesión nuevamente
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="text-center mt-4">
                        <p class="text-muted">¿Necesitas ayuda? <a href="#" class="text-primary">Contacta con soporte</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        // Redirección opcional tras 5s
        setTimeout(function () {
            window.location.href = '@Url.Action("InicioSesion", "Login")';
        }, 5000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>